videos.description: Kyle  Washington makes contested push shot. Extends Bearcats run to 6-0.
videos.headline: Kyle Washington hits off-balance push shot

videos.description: Bearcats steal leads to Jacob Evans' one-man fast break as he finishes with a nice layup at the rim.
videos.headline: Jacob Evans with the smooth finish around the basket

videos.description: The Bearcats' interior defense holds firm as Kyle Washington blocks the Tulsa shot attempt.
videos.headline: Kyle Washington with the big-time rejection.

videos.description: Gary Clark takes the entry pass from Kyle Washington and delivers the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Gary Clark hammers home the dunk

videos.description: Adam Faust throws to Mike Wise who interviews Bearcats HC Mick Cronin about winning his 300th game as a head coach
videos.headline: Post-game breakdown discusses Cincinnati's runaway victory over Tulsa that gave coach Mick Cronin his 300th Division 1 Victory
